text: Miho Hashiguchi (born 29 December 1977) is a Japanese gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aichi Prefecture Category:Asian Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Gymnasts at the 1998 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Japan Category:Medalists at the 1998 Asian Games
